data.description: This home also qualifies for the 100% USDA loan for qualified buyers! This single owner home has it all!  Built in 2019, this 4 bedroom 2 1/2 bath gem is in the highly desired Ridgeville Crossings neighborhood with Spartanburg county District 2 schools. The front porch welcomes you into this bright open floor plan with mountain views, and lots of premium upgrades throughout. Gorgeous granite countertops, stainless appliances, walk-in pantry and breakfast bar compose the kitchen nicely.  Beautiful LVT flooring throughout the main floor! All four bedrooms and the laundry room are located on the second floor.  The master suite has mountain views, large bathroom with a garden tub, glass shower, dual sinks and a walk-in closet. There is a loft in the midst of the bedrooms that can be enjoyed as a reading nook, kids play area, gaming or study area. The other 3 bedrooms share a full bathroom with a dual sink vanity. The laundry room is on the same floor as all the bedrooms making your tasks a little easier. A very nice sized flat yard to enjoy with family and friends. You may also hang out and swim in the beautiful neighborhood swimming pool that has bathrooms and a large covered patio area. The location is ideal with easy access to I-26 & I-85 and is centrally located between Greenville, Spartanburg and Asheville.  Just minutes from Lake Bowen, Woodfin Ridge Golf Club and Publix! A brand-new Target is coming less than 5 miles down SC-9!  You don’t want to wait on this one….bring your pickiest buyers!
